<pb ed="X" xml:id="X74.1470.0243b" n="0243b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0243b01"/><lb ed="R128" n="0485a04"/><p xml:id="pX74p0243b0101"><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0243001" n="0243001"/>經云爾時智首菩薩<note place="inline">至</note>以一切聲聞緣覺所不能動。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0243b02"/><lb ed="R128" n="0485a05"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0243b0201"><l>願共諸眾生</l><l>往生華藏海</l><l>極樂淨土中</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0243b03"/><lb ed="R128" n="0485a06"/><list><item xml:id="itemX74p0243b0301"><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0243002" n="0243002"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0243002" n="0243002"/>南無大方廣佛華嚴經中華藏世界海十身無礙本
<lb ed="X" n="0243b04"/><lb ed="R128" n="0485a07"/>尊毗盧遮那佛</item>
